{"id":2269,"date":"2024-11-24T20:23:09","date_gmt":"2024-11-24T20:23:09","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=2269"},"modified":"2024-11-25T22:11:58","modified_gmt":"2024-11-25T22:11:58","slug":"pep-quiz-house","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/extras\/pep-quiz-house\/","title":{"rendered":"Pep Quiz House (Magnolia Town)"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>The Magnolia Town\u2019s Pep Quiz House is a small wooden house located at the east end of town, right next to the Pokecenter. It features a daily trivia mini-game where you answer short questions and receive a reward for the correct ones.<\/p>\n<p>The table below details each question asked by \u2018Aha\u2019, the host of the quiz, along with the correct answer for them.<\/p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table grey left zebra\" style=\"min-width:350px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Question<\/th>\n<th>Hint Given<\/th>\n<th>Answer<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>What color are the bridges on Route 8?<\/td>\n<td>They\u2019re not white!<\/td>\n<td>Brown<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What does the \u201cT\u201d in \u201cKBT Expressway\u201d stand for?<\/td>\n<td>It\u2019s a long word!<\/td>\n<td>Third<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Which type of Pokemon is the most common?<\/td>\n<td>There is too much of it!<\/td>\n<td>Water<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Which Pokemon is born from temperatures and pressures deep underground?<\/td>\n<td>Its body is hard like diamonds!<\/td>\n<td>Carbink<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What single-type Pokemon is known as The Cave Pokemon?<\/td>\n<td>It\u2019s not a Rock- or Ground-Type!<\/td>\n<td>Druddigon<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>The famous ruins in West Borrius are known as the Ruins of what?<\/td>\n<td>They\u2019re not the Ruins of Alph!<\/td>\n<td>Void<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Who are the mysterious creatures that inhabit our world?<\/td>\n<td>They\u2019re not Pokemon!<\/td>\n<td>Women<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What was the original wing colour of a Shiny Charizard?<\/td>\n<td>It\u2019s not Red!<\/td>\n<td>Green<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What is a two-on-two Pokemon battle called?<\/td>\n<td>If it\u2019s a one-on-one battle, it\u2019s a Single!<\/td>\n<td>Double<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>What\u2019s my daughter\u2019s name?<\/td>\n<td>It\u2019s not Smeargle!<\/td>\n<td>Ditoh<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<h2>Quiz House Location<\/h2>\n<p>From the Magnolia Town Pokecenter, just go into the house directly to your right. The Pep Quiz is hosted in the small wooden house here. <\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/01-pokemon-unbound-outside-the-pep-quiz-house.jpg\" alt=\"Outside the Pep Quiz House \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Outside the Pep Quiz House<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>Prizes<\/h2>\n<p>Aha rewards you for each question you answer correctly (or incorrectly). <\/p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\">\n<table class=\"table grey left\" style=\"min-width:350px;\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Condition<\/th>\n<th>Prize<\/th>\n<th>Reaction<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Answer Correctly<\/td>\n<td>Big Nugget<\/td>\n<td>\n<figure class=\"img-modal\"><a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-prize-big-nugget.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/02-pokemon-unbound-prize-big-nugget.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Answer Incorrectly<\/td>\n<td>Tiny Mushroom<\/td>\n<td>\n<figure class=\"img-modal\"><a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-prize-tiny-mushroom.jpg\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/11\/03-pokemon-unbound-prize-tiny-mushroom.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a><\/figure>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<\/div>\n<h2>Key Information<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>The Pep Quiz can be done once every 24 hours.<\/li>\n<li>The questions asked by Aha follow no particular sequence and will be chosen randomly. They can also be repeated. <\/li>\n<li>Your answers do not have to be case sensitive.<\/li>\n<li>The quiz starts as soon as you enter the house and can be attempted each day indefinitely.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/extras\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/10\/kyurem-unbound-sidequest.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/10\/kyurem-unbound-sidequest.jpg 300w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/10\/kyurem-unbound-sidequest-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Extras &#038; Side-Quests<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":2270,"parent":1980,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[],"class_list":["post-2269","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/2269","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1980"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/227